							<h1>
								Marie Curie Helper Service
							</h1>
							<p class="lead">
								We know the little things can make a big difference when you, or someone you care about, are living with a terminal illness.
								<h2>Find a Marie Curie Helper</h2>
							<p class="lead">Having someone to chat to over a cup of tea, help you get to an appointment or run an errand, or just be there to listen when you need a friendly ear.</p>
						</header>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
